[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]首宗'''[[人類免疫缺乏病毒|艾滋病毒]]感染{{Notetag|艾滋病（AIDS），即[[获得性免疫缺陷综合征|获得性免疫缺陷综合征]]，是艾滋病毒感染的最后阶段。艾滋病毒即HIV，亦即[[人类免疫缺陷病毒|人类免疫缺陷病毒]]<ref name="who2017aids">{{Cite web|title=艾滋病毒/艾滋病相关问答|url=https://www.who.int/features/qa/71/zh/|work=|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]|date=2017-11|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418195107/https://www.who.int/features/qa/71/zh/|archive-date=2019-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。HIV/AIDS即HIV感染和艾滋病的合并写法。|name=HIVAIDS}}'''报告于1985年，首例报道感染者为一名來自[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]的美國游客，在[[北京协和医院|北京协和医院]]因并发病逝世。[[中國科學院|中國科學院]]院士[[曾毅_(病毒学家)|曾毅]]依据血清檢測显示，已知作为艾滋病病原的HIV最早於1982年以进口血液制品形式進入中國大陸，並於1983年开始感染[[中华人民共和国公民|中华人民共和国公民]]。1990年代，艾滋病疫情呈现快速增长态势，主要集中于[[云南省|云南]]边境吸毒者群体中，并且逐渐以各种传播方式扩散到了全国各地，形成了第一波HIV流行。由于政府医疗部门对疾病认知不足、行政部门渎职瞒报等多方面原因，造成了以[[河南血祸|河南血祸]]为代表的第二波HIV流行。

1990年代初，[[中華人民共和國政府|中華人民共和國政府]]开始组织成立部门防治中国大陆地区艾滋病疫情，1990年代末通过法规和防治计划开始控制疫情，但2000年代初，中国大陆政府官员多次承认艾滋病疫情快速增长之态势<ref>{{Cite news|title=China Now Facing an Aids Epidemic, a Top Aide Admits|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/08/24/world/china-now-facing-an-aids-epidemic-a-top-aide-admits.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2001-08-24|accessdate=2019-05-07|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Elisabeth|last=Rosenthal|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507023716/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/08/24/world/china-now-facing-an-aids-epidemic-a-top-aide-admits.html|archive-date=2019-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":14">{{Cite journal|title=China admits its AIDS crisis|author=|url=https://www.bmj.com/content/323/7315/714.1|last=Plafker|first=Ted|date=2001-09-29|journal=BMJ|issue=7315|doi=10.1136/bmj.323.7315.714|others=|year=|volume=323|page=|pages=714|language=en|issn=0959-8138|pmc=1121282|pmid=11576976|access-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507023716/https://www.bmj.com/content/323/7315/714.1|archive-date=2019-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2002/WORLD/asiapcf/east/04/11/china.aids/|title=China admits AIDS rising sharply|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2002-04-11|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|language=en-US|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507023716/http://edition.cnn.com/2002/WORLD/asiapcf/east/04/11/china.aids/|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>。中国政府对HIV/AIDS的态度从否认转为重视疫情对于人民的威胁<ref name=":80">{{Cite journal|title=Securitizing HIV/AIDS: a game changer in state-societal relations in China?|author=|url=https://doi.org/10.1186/s12992-018-0364-7|last=Lo|first=Catherine Yuk-ping|date=2018-05-16|journal=Globalization and Health|issue=1|doi=10.1186/s12992-018-0364-7|others=|year=|volume=14|page=|pages=50|issn=1744-8603|pmc=5956947|pmid=29769102}}</ref>，艾滋病疫情控制取得可观进步<ref name=":16">{{Cite journal|title=China's pragmatic approach to AIDS.|author=|url=https://www.who.int/bulletin/volumes/84/4/news10406/en/|last=Parry|first=Jane|date=|journal=Bulletin of the World Health Organization|issue=4|doi=|others=|year=2006|volume=84|page=|pages=261–262|issn=0042-9686|pmid=16628294|access-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180430232440/http://www.who.int/bulletin/volumes/84/4/news10406/en/|archive-date=2018-04-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.avert.org/professionals/hiv-around-world/asia-pacific/china|title=HIV and AIDS in China|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-07-21|work=[[AVERT|AVERT]]|publisher=|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321023043/https://www.avert.org/professionals/hiv-around-world/asia-pacific/china|archive-date=2019-03-21|others=(最后[[同行評審|评议]]于2016-12-12)}}</ref><ref name=":58">{{Cite journal|title=China AIDS policy implementation: reversing the HIV/AIDS epidemic by 2015|author=|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2992622/|last=Wu|first=Zunyou|last2=Wang|first2=Yu|date=2010-12|journal=International Journal of Epidemiology|issue=Suppl 2|doi=10.1093/ije/dyq220|others=|year=|volume=39|page=|pages=ii1–ii3|issn=0300-5771|pmc=2992622|pmid=21113031|last3=Detels|first3=Roger|last4=Rotheram-Borus|first4=Mary Jane|access-date=2019-05-11|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215011255/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2992622/}}</ref>。根据[[中国疾病预防控制中心|中国疾控中心]]、[[联合国艾滋病联合规划署|联合国艾滋病规划署]]、[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]联合报告估算{{Notetag|name=联合报告|中国卫生部门和联合国的艾滋病监测合作自2000年代初即展开，每年发布一份联合报告<ref name=":55"/>。本条目中简称为“联合报告”。}}，至2018年年底，中国大陆存活艾滋病感染者约125万，流行率为万分之9，整体疫情处于低流行水平<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-11/23/content_5342852.htm|title=国家卫健委：我国艾滋病全人群感染率约万分之九|accessdate=2019-05-06|author=|date=2018-11-23|work=|publisher=[[中华人民共和国中央人民政府门户网站|中华人民共和国中央人民政府]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506140233/http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-11/23/content_5342852.htm|archive-date=2019-05-06}}</ref>，但感染者的数量仍然巨大<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100066121.html|title=中国已能药物控制艾滋病传染，问题是每年有30%感染者没被发现|accessdate=2019-05-06|author=马晓华|date=2018-11-28|work=|publisher=[[第一财经|第一财经]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508094328/https://www.yicai.com/news/100066121.html|archive-date=2019-05-08}}</ref>。随着艾滋病检测范围的扩大，报告新发感染人数逐年增加，2017年达到13.5万人，另估计约有三成病患对自身患病不知情<ref name=":3" />。2017年，收报艾滋病的主要传播途径以[[人类性行为|异性性行为]]为主，占约七成，[[人类性行为|同性性行为]]其次，占约二成半，母婴传播和输血传播已经基本阻断<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://jiankang.cctv.com/2018/11/23/ARTIziC0gNBTLkOTPJsGrUbf181123.shtml|title=我国艾滋病防控工作成效显著 基本阻断输血传播|accessdate=2019-05-06|author=邹杨|date=2018-11-23|work=|publisher=[[央视网|央视网]]|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506140233/http://jiankang.cctv.com/2018/11/23/ARTIziC0gNBTLkOTPJsGrUbf181123.shtml|archive-date=2019-05-06}}</ref>。2017年接受[[抗病毒药物|抗病毒治疗]]者达到61万人，但是推广治疗带来的病毒[[耐药性|耐药性]]问题引发了新的担忧<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":29">{{Cite journal|title=Emerging Trends of HIV Drug Resistance in Chinese HIV-Infected Patients Receiving First-Line Highly Active Antiretroviral Therapy: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis|url=https://academic.oup.com/cid/article/59/10/1495/2895326|last=Wang|first=Ning|last2=Zhu|first2=Lin|date=2014-11-15|journal=Clinical Infectious Diseases|issue=10|doi=10.1093/cid/ciu590|volume=59|pages=1495–1502|language=en|issn=1058-4838|last3=Wu|first3=Jing|last4=Gu|first4=Hongqiu|last5=Jin|first5=Yantao|last6=Liu|first6=Ying|last7=Smith|first7=M. Kumi|last8=Su|first8=Yingying|last9=Ma|first9=Ye|author=|access-date=2019-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509130530/https://academic.oup.com/cid/article/59/10/1495/2895326|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

艾滋病作为[[污名認同|污名化]]的社会疾病，在世界各地产生了社会恐惧<ref name=":30">{{Cite journal|title=艾滋病、污名和社会歧视:中国乡村社区中两类人群的一个定量分析|author=刘能|url=http://www.cqvip.com/QK/80772X/200506/20734865.html|journal=社会学研究|issue=6|doi=|others=|year=2005|volume=|page=136-164|pmid=|access-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135049/http://www.cqvip.com/QK/80772X/200506/20734865.html|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ogden">{{cite web|vauthors=Ogden J, Nyblade L|website=International Center for Research on Women|year=2005|title=Common at its core: HIV-related stigma across contexts|url=http://www.icrw.org/docs/2005_report_stigma_synthesis.pdf|access-date=2007-02-15|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FEwkK8ZU?url=http://www.icrw.org/publications/common-its-core-hiv-related-stigma-across-contexts|archive-date=2013-03-19|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=}}</ref>；艾滋病相关议题在[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]曾是，或现在仍然是一个敏感话题<ref name=":31">{{Cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2166247/chinas-aids-orphans-better-investment-banker-who-turned-his-back|title=‘I was lucky, they weren’t’: why a Wall Street banker quit to help Aids orphans|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=Alice, Yan|date=2018-09-30|work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]]|publisher=|language=en|dead-url=no|quote=Both the government and domestic media don’t think HIV is a sensitive issue now and there are no problems in that regard, he said.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190312180309/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2166247/chinas-aids-orphans-better-investment-banker-who-turned-his-back|archive-date=2019-03-12}}</ref><ref name=":32">{{Cite news|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/gongyi/2017-06/28/c_129642629.htm|title=首例“艾滋病就业歧视案”：当事人曾被劝以卵击石|author=|date=2017-06-28|work=[[中国青年报|中国青年报]]|accessdate=2019-05-09|quote=在办理案件过程中，合议庭发现社会公众对艾滋病的认知尚有较大局限，谈‘艾’色变、‘恐艾症’等情况在一定范围内广泛存在。”广州市中院民事审判庭庭长、本案审判长陈冬梅坦言，话题的敏感对合议庭是一个不小的压力。|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135050/http://www.xinhuanet.com/gongyi/2017-06/28/c_129642629.htm|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":33">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gzywca.org/Project/hiv.html|title=编织爱的红丝带——广州基督教女青年会艾滋病干预项目侧记|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=广州基督教女青年会|date=|publisher=|quote=由于艾滋病本身的特殊性和敏感性，社区内存在这样一群特殊的感染者：他们很少主动参与检测或关怀项目，社区卫生人员也长期无法与他们取得联系。|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135050/http://www.gzywca.org/Project/hiv.html|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":34">{{Cite book|title=在公路建设背景下实施艾滋病预防——中华人民共和国广西壮族自治区案例研究|last=|first=|publisher=亚洲开发银行|year=2014|isbn=978-92-9254-587-1|location=菲律宾曼达卢永市|pages=7-9|url=https://www.adb.org/sites/default/files/publication/81966/implementing-hiv-prevention-zh.pdf|quote=谈及非常个人的行为时，HIV是一个敏感话题。|access-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030020700/http://www.adb.org/sites/default/files/publication/81966/implementing-hiv-prevention-zh.pdf|archive-date=2015-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":35">{{Cite web|title=中国“草根组织”渐成防治艾滋病宣传生力军|url=http://fjjsw.fjsen.com/2013-12/02/content_13076956.htm|work=中国新闻网西安|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=冽玮; 张一辰|date=2013-12-02|publisher=|via=福建人口计生新闻网|quote=自1985年内地发现首例艾滋病患者以来，艾滋病一度成为讳莫如深的敏感话题。|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135051/http://fjjsw.fjsen.com/2013-12/02/content_13076956.htm|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":36">{{Cite news|url=http://www.aviationnow.com.cn/Page/News_details.aspx?id=a5899752dcc4810dcccd74a8f315590f|title=国内九大航企：对艾滋病患者不拒载不歧视|author=|date=2014-08-01|work=辽沈晚报|accessdate=|quote=本报记者昨日先后与国内9家航空公司取得联系，针对这一敏感话题，他们的表态一致：不会拒绝艾滋病患者登机。|via=航空在线|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203112440/http://www.aviationnow.com.cn/Page/News_details.aspx?id=a5899752dcc4810dcccd74a8f315590f}}</ref>，尽管包括政府在内的各界尝试减少对患者的歧视<ref name=":38">{{Cite web|title=China struggles to face reality of AIDS|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20081204-china-struggles-face-reality-aids-|work=France 24|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2019-05-09|language=en|author=|publisher=|quote=AIDS is still a highly sensitive topic in China despite the government's attempts to be open about the subject.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135050/https://www.france24.com/en/20081204-china-struggles-face-reality-aids-|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，医护机构工作人员在内的社会大众对HIV携带者的歧视仍然普遍存在<ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title=HIV/Aids patients still face rejection and discrimination in China’s leading hospitals|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/policies-politics/article/2006640/hiv/aids-patients-still-face-rejection-and|work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]]|date=2016-08-20|accessdate=2019-05-07|language=en|author=Yan, Alice|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180429114728/http://www.scmp.com/news/china/policies-politics/article/2006640/hiv/aids-patients-still-face-rejection-and|archive-date=2018-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。媒体亦对艾滋病患者存在歧视<ref name=":40">{{Cite journal|title=大众传媒对我国艾滋病污名化的影响研究|author=赵云云|url=http://www.wanfangdata.com.cn/details/detail.do?_type=degree&id=D495104#|date=2014-09-17|journal=山西师范大学|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|pmid=|access-date=2019-05-09|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521041101/http://www.wanfangdata.com.cn/details/detail.do?_type=degree&id=D495104}}</ref>。为数不小的公众对艾滋病有种强烈的恐惧情绪，形成了“恐艾症患者”群体<ref name=":43">{{Cite web|title=未被阳光照射到的“恐艾”群体|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2268059|work=澎湃新闻|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=栾心怡; 位梦; 蔡鸿坚; 辛成龙; 方洁|date=2018-08-03|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135049/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2268059|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

