pages=286–287|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=21322842}}</ref><ref name=":24">{{Cite journal|title=HIV-related stigma and discrimination amongst healthcare providers in Guangzhou, China|author=|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6003171/|last=Dong|first=Xiaomei|last2=Yang|first2=Jianwei|date=2018-06-15|journal=BMC Public Health|issue=|doi=10.1186/s12889-018-5654-8|others=|year=|volume=18|page=|issn=1471-2458|pmc=6003171|pmid=29902990|last3=Peng|first3=Lin|last4=Pang|first4=Minhui|last5=Zhang|first5=Jiayi|last6=Zhang|first6=Zhan|last7=Rao|first7=Jiaming|last8=Wang|first8=Haiqing|last9=Chen|first9=Xiongfei|access-date=2019-05-07|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215021336/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6003171/}}</ref>，并且形成了一批“恐艾症”群体<ref name=":42">{{Cite news|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/wencui/social/story20161129-696077|title=中国至少有五六十万恐艾患者 因担心感染饱受折磨|author=|date=2016-11-29|work=[[中国青年报|中国青年报]]|accessdate=2019-05-09|via=[[联合早报|联合早报]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135047/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/wencui/social/story20161129-696077|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":43">{{Cite web|title=未被阳光照射到的“恐艾”群体|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2268059|work=澎湃新闻|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=栾心怡; 位梦; 蔡鸿坚; 辛成龙; 方洁|date=2018-08-03|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135049/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2268059|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":44">{{Cite web|title=美容针灸后患上“恐艾症” 女高管几乎无法工作|url=https://e.thecover.cn/shtml/hxdsb/20171201/63673.shtml|work=华西都市报|accessdate=2019-05-09|author=杜江茜|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509135053/https://e.thecover.cn/shtml/hxdsb/20171201/63673.shtml|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。媒体依然存在对于艾滋病患者的歧视现象<ref name=":39">{{Cite journal|title=我国艾滋病相关歧视现状研究及策略建议|author=张丽坪; 徐鹏; 吕繁|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-XBYA201105048.htm|journal=中国艾滋病性病|issue=5|doi=|others=|year=2011|volume=|page=|pmid=|access-date=2019-05-09|archive-date=2021-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907085449/http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-XBYA201105048.htm}}</ref><ref name=":40">{{Cite journal|title=大众传媒对我国艾滋病污名化的影响研究|author=赵云云|url=http://www.wanfangdata.com.cn/details/detail.do?_type=degree&id=D495104#|date=2014-09-17|journal=山西师范大学|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|pmid=}}</ref><ref name=":41">{{Cite journal|title=媒体记者艾滋病防治知识及信息传播渠道调查|author=夏庆华; 胡晓云; 徐静东|url=http://xueshu.baidu.com/usercenter/paper/show?paperid=56fc50ac9177fa7af899c5462d9a20a9&site=xueshu_se&sc_from=zju|journal=公共卫生与预防医学|issue=2|doi=10.3969/j.issn.1006-2483.2007.02.009|others=|year=2007|volume=18|page=27-29|pmid=|access-date=2019-05-09|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215013042/https://xueshu.baidu.com/usercenter/paper/show?paperid=56fc50ac9177fa7af899c5462d9a20a9&site=xueshu_se&sc_from=zju}}</ref>。

1980年代艾滋病开始在西方国家出现时，中国舆论将之与西方资本主义挂钩，感染者往往会被贴上外国人或者中国社会之外的标签<ref name=":71">{{Cite book|chapter=HIV-Related Stigma and Discrimination in China: A Persistent Puzzle|title=HIV/AIDS in China: Beyond the Numbers|series=Public Health in China|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-10-3746-7_8|publisher=Springer Singapore|date=2017|location=Singapore|isbn=9789811037467|pages=95–107|doi=10.1007/978-981-10-3746-7_8|language=en|first=Anuradha|last=Chaddah|first2=Zunyou|last2=Wu|editor-first=Zunyou|editor-last=Wu}}</ref>。早期公共卫生警告往往宣传宣传其恐怖，并将疾病与外国与同性恋挂钩<ref name=":71" />。但是首批感染者却发生在偏远农村的农民当中，其中还有许多是少数民族<ref name=":71" />。尽管处于疫情处于低流行态势，艾滋病疫情的扩散依然引起大众及媒体的关注，并引起过2010年取消艾滋病患者入境限制以及[[男男性行為|男男性行为]]增加导致艾滋病疫情扩大化的谣言<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/246634/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%81%90%E6%88%90-%E6%84%9B%E6%BB%8B%E7%97%85%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B-%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B7%E7%94%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%BF%AB%E4%BA%A4|title=中國恐成「愛滋病大國」 因男男同性戀及染病非洲留學生濫交？|author=葉琪|date=2018-10-14|work=香港01|accessdate=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028073842/https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/246634/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%81%90%E6%88%90-%E6%84%9B%E6%BB%8B%E7%97%85%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B-%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B7%E7%94%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%BF%AB%E4%BA%A4|archive-date=2018-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2664335|title=取消艾滋病入境限制致感染者暴增？实际是统计规则有大调整|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=赵孟; 胡丹萍|date=2018-11-23|work=澎湃新闻|publisher=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507025218/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_2664335|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>。网络和媒体流传的有关官员患艾滋病的[[性醜聞|性醜聞]]，曾引起过民众恐慌和媒体关注<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20150403/bkncn-20150403173109523-0403_05011_001_cn.html|title=网传公共情妇汤灿患爱滋 惹中央高层恐慌|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-04-03|work=on.cc東網|publisher=|language=zh-hk|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028074028/https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20150403/bkncn-20150403173109523-0403_05011_001_cn.html|archive-date=2018-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2486694|title=中國貪官驚爆愛滋 當地女教師、女公務員急衝醫院|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2018-07-12|work=自由時報電子報|publisher=|language=zh-tw|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112034938/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2486694|archive-date=2018-11-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180802/1402912/|title=強國高官傳集體買處 國中妹染性病「涉案近百人」|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2018-08-02|work=蘋果新聞網|publisher=|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618190222/https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180802/1402912/}}</ref>。{{Quote box
