2017年，[[浙江省中医院|浙江省中医院]]一名技术人员违反“一人一管一抛弃”操作规程，在操作中重复使用吸管造成交叉污染，造成重大医疗事故，经疾控机构检测确诊5例感染者<ref name=":20">{{Cite news|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/legal/2018-06/12/c_1122971072.htm|title=致5人染艾滋病毒 违规医生被判刑|author=张雅|date=2018-06-12|work=[[北京青年报|北京青年报]]|accessdate=2019-05-06|via=[[新华网|新华网]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404171409/http://www.xinhuanet.com/legal/2018-06/12/c_1122971072.htm|archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Five infected with HIV after dirty needles used at China hospital|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/article/2069424/least-five-infected-hiv-after-dirty-needles-used-chinese-hospital|work=South China Morning Post|date=2017-02-09|accessdate=2019-05-07|language=en|author=Jun Mai|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084835/https://www.scmp.com/news/article/2069424/least-five-infected-hiv-after-dirty-needles-used-chinese-hospital|archive-date=2019-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>；事后，涉事技术员被刑事拘留、立案调查，最终因[[醫療事故|医疗事故罪]]判处获刑2年6个月，时任院长、副院长、检验科主任等被免职<ref name=":20" />。

对涉事医生的法院判决文书显示，2016年12月30日上午，涉案技术员进行“封闭抗体治疗”项目期间抱持侥幸心理，违反“一人一管一抛弃”操作规程操作，2017年1月24日接受项目的一女子告知主治医师其丈夫因个人原因感染HIV，涉案技术员了解后自知危险而上报，至2017年2月确认5名HIV感染者<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2018-06-11/doc-ihcufqih0485442.shtml|title=浙江一医生违规操作致5人染艾滋病毒案判决公布：获刑两年半|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=2018-06-11|last=|work=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|publisher=|via=[[新浪网|新浪网]]|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821152944/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2018-06-11/doc-ihcufqih0485442.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 窗口期输血 ====
{{Main|福建女童输血感染艾滋病事件}}
2014年9月，福建一五岁女童血液检验呈现HIV阳性，疑似因四年前心脏手术在医院输血导致<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2015-01/11/content_19290789.htm|title=Girl infected with HIV from heart operation: official|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-01-11|work=|publisher=[[新华社|Xinhua]]|dead-url=no|via=China Daily|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084827/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2015-01/11/content_19290789.htm|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>。官方调查事后发现输血血样中有一例阳性样本，与献血者复查后证实艾滋病病毒感染：这些结果显示该女童大概率为艾滋病窗口期感染，且认定医院和血液中心均无法律上的不当行为<ref name=":18">{{Cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/5-year-old-girl-in-china-got-hiv-through-blood-transfusion-report|title=5-year-old girl in China got HIV through blood transfusion: Report|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-01-12|last=|work=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]|publisher=|language=en|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084833/https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/5-year-old-girl-in-china-got-hiv-through-blood-transfusion-report|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref><ref name=":19">{{Cite web|url=http://news.sohu.com/20150111/n407694836.shtml|title=福建5岁女童因输血感染艾滋 献血者称不知情|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=余伟利;侯振海;江永韬|date=2015-01-11|work=[[中国中央电视台|央视]]新闻|publisher=|dead-url=no|via=[[搜狐|搜狐]]网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084835/http://news.sohu.com/20150111/n407694836.shtml|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>。两家涉事单位进行了77万人民币的补偿<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1345315|title=福建女童输血染艾滋获赔77万，涉事单位重申系无过错意外|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-06-25|work=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|publisher=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084829/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1345315|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2015/06-25/7366496.shtml|title=福建女童输血染艾滋获赔77万：系无过错医疗意外|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=詹托荣;李章亮;邹家骅|date=2015-06-25|work=[[人民网|人民网]]|publisher=|dead-url=no|via=中国新闻网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084832/http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2015/06-25/7366496.shtml|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>。事件引发对输血安全的担忧<ref name=":18" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/opinion/2015-01/14/content_19317306.htm|title=China should ensure safe blood supply|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=|date=2015-01-14|last=Chelala|first=Cesar|work=[[China_Daily|China Daily]]|publisher=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084838/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/opinion/2015-01/14/content_19317306.htm|archive-date=2019-05-07}}</ref>，以及对窗口期输血导致事故的责任等相关法律规章进行修改的争议<ref name=":65">{{Cite web|title=从输血感染艾滋病谈患者权益保护|url=https://www.chinacourt.org/article/detail/2015/01/id/1536124.shtml|work=中国法院网|accessdate=2019-05-07|author=黄腾|date=2015-01-19|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507084840/https://www.chinacourt.org/article/detail/2015/01/id/1536124.shtml|archive-date=2019-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":19" />。

