=== 行业监管 ===
{{参见|上海新兴医药血液制品污染事件}}

2019年2月5日，中国大陆媒体报道上海新兴医药股份有限公司生产批次为20180610z的静脉注射人免疫球蛋白呈现HIV抗体阳性<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://economics.dwnews.com/news/2019-02-05/60116857.html|title=中国再爆医疗事故 上海药企静注产品艾滋病抗体阳性|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=2019-02-05|work=[[多维新闻网|多维新闻网]]|publisher=|archive-date=2019-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121163145/http://economics.dwnews.com/news/2019-02-05/60116857.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=中国医药子企业血制品染艾惊魂的来龙去脉|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47153737|date=2019-02-07|accessdate=2019-05-11|language=|author=|work=[[BBC|BBC]]中文网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501152424/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-47153737|archive-date=2019-05-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/china-tests-show-no-hiv-in-tainted-medical-item|title=China: Tests show no HIV in 'tainted' medical item|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=2019-02-08|last=|work=[[路透社|REUTERS]]|publisher=|language=en|via=[[海峡时报|The Straits Times]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301225725/https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/china-tests-show-no-hiv-in-tainted-medical-item|archive-date=2019-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。依据[[经济观察报|经济观察网]]报道，事件追溯到江西一位新生儿检出HIV弱阳性，依照追溯体系追查到上海新兴医药，同年1月15日，[[国家药品监督管理局|国家药品监督管理局]]发布《关于修订静注人[[抗体|免疫球蛋白]]和冻干静注人免疫球蛋白说明书的公告》，在其中警示：原料由人血采集，生产理论上可以消除病毒传播危害，但无法完全消除隐患，应当谨慎使用<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eeo.com.cn/2019/0206/347433.shtml|title=【独家】上海新兴医药静注人免疫球蛋白还未立案 同批次原料的其他血液产品未检测出艾滋病阳性|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=温淑萍|date=2019-02-06|work=[[经济观察网|经济观察网]]|publisher=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207132721/http://www.eeo.com.cn/2019/0206/347433.shtml|archive-date=2019-02-07}}</ref>。据财新网报道，行业人士指出，工业产生中通常会经过病毒去除和失活，因此出现感染的概率较低<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.caixinglobal.com/2019-02-07/china-investigates-reports-of-hiv-contaminated-pharmaceutical-products-101377952.html|title=China Investigates Reports of HIV-Contaminated Pharmaceutical Products|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=|work=[[财新网|Caixin Global]]|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215013751/https://www.caixinglobal.com/2019-02-07/china-investigates-reports-of-hiv-contaminated-pharmaceutical-products-101377952.html}}</ref>。据[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]转述业内人士，批评涉事企业未做好血液检测，安全隐患极大，该电台亦证实常规操作流程下较难出现病毒<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/hiv-02062019063141.html|title=央企血液制品疑用艾滋血源 过万剂「人用」免疫球蛋白被污染|accessdate=2019-05-11|work=Radio Free Asia|language=zh-yue|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208170000/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/hiv-02062019063141.html|archive-date=2019-02-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，涉事产品被查封，并被要求检测<ref name=":72">{{Cite news|title=Chinese Regulators Examine Xinxing's Blood Products for HIV|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-02-06/china-regulators-investigating-shanghai-xinxing-s-blood-products|date=2019-02-06|accessdate=2019-05-11|language=en|author=Cao, Belinda|work=[[彭博新聞社|Bloomberg]]|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124165344/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-02-06/china-regulators-investigating-shanghai-xinxing-s-blood-products}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thediplomat.com/2019/02/china-investigates-blood-plasma-products-potentially-tainted-with-hiv/|title=China Investigates Blood Plasma Products Potentially Tainted With HIV|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=|last=Tiezzi|first=Shannon|work=[[外交家_(雜誌)|The Diplomat]]|publisher=|language=en-US|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220141934/https://thediplomat.com/2019/02/china-investigates-blood-plasma-products-potentially-tainted-with-hiv/|archive-date=2019-02-20}}</ref>。2月6日，[[国家食品药品监督管理局|国家药监局]]发文称涉事药品和涉事儿童均未检出HIV阳性<ref name=":72" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nmpa.gov.cn/WS04/CL2056/334991.html|title=国家药监局公布上海新兴相关产品初步调查情况|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=国家药监局|date=2019-02-06|work=|publisher=|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215013826/https://www.nmpa.gov.cn/WS04/CL2056/334991.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2185275/chinese-blood-plasma-cleared-authorities-give-mixed-messages-hiv|title=Chinese blood plasma ‘clear’ of HIV as authorities give mixed messages|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=Wong, Michelle|date=2019-02-07|work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]]|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506064825/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/2185275/chinese-blood-plasma-cleared-authorities-give-mixed-messages-hiv|archive-date=2019-05-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月10日晚间，上市企业[[中国医药|中国医药]]称已经受政府命令已经停产旗下公司上海新兴相关批号药品<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bioon.com/article/6733465.html|title=上海新兴已全面停产核查|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=2019-02-11|last=王一鸣|work=证券时报|publisher=|via=生物谷|archive-date=2020-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525070512/http://news.bioon.com/article/6733465.html}}</ref>。

